# Title: Kubernetes Rolebinding Modification
# Author: kelnage
# Date: 2024-07-11
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects when a Kubernetes Rolebinding is created or modified.
# MITRE Tactic: Privilege Escalation
# Tags: attack.privilege-escalation
# False Positives:
#   - Modifying a Kubernetes Rolebinding may need to be done by a system administrator.
#   - Automated processes may need to take these actions and may need to be filtered.

objectRef.apiGroup="rbac.authorization.k8s.io" objectRef.resource IN ("clusterrolebindings", "rolebindings") verb IN ("create", "delete", "patch", "replace", "update")